snippet.title: Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed DLC #2 Teaser
snippet.description:
DLC 2 is here and it's FREE! Enter the S.C.Y. County Courthouse, if you dare. 
The demonic Possessor Ghost Type is a beast-like monster with extreme brute force that can sniff out a scared Buster like a slab of rotting beef!

Get all the details here:
https://www.ghostbusterssu.com/news/

Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed is available on PC on EPIC GAMES, PS4™, PS4™Pro, PS5™, Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One. To learn more about the game visit: https://www.ghostbusterssu.com/
